{"id":488,"ayahs":[{"number":45,"arabic":"وَتَرَىٰهُمْ يُعْرَضُونَ عَلَيْهَا خَٰشِعِينَ مِنَ ٱلذُّلِّ يَنظُرُونَ مِن طَرْفٍ خَفِىٍّۢ ۗ وَقَالَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوٓا۟ إِنَّ ٱلْخَٰسِرِينَ ٱلَّذِينَ خَسِرُوٓا۟ أَنفُسَهُمْ وَأَهْلِيهِمْ يَوْمَ ٱلْقِيَٰمَةِ ۗ أَلَآ إِنَّ ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ فِى عَذَابٍۢ مُّقِيمٍۢ","translation":"And thou wilt see them exposed to that [doom], humbling themselves in abasement, looking [around] with a furtive glance - the while those who had attained to faith will say, “Verily, lost on [this] Day of Resurrection are they who have squandered their own and their followers’ selves!” Oh, verily, the evildoers will fall into long-lasting suffering,","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4317.mp3","surahId":42,"words":[{"id":44976,"position":1,"arabic":"وَتَرَىٰهُمْ","translation":"এবং  তাদের দেখবে তুমি","audioUrl":"wbw/042_045_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44977,"position":2,"arabic":"يُعْرَضُونَ","translation":"উপস্থিত করা হচ্ছে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_045_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44978,"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْهَا","translation":"তার (অর্থাৎ জাহান্নামের) কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_045_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44979,"position":4,"arabic":"خَـٰشِعِينَ","translation":"অবনত হয়ে থাকবে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_045_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44980,"position":5,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"কারণে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_045_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44981,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلذُّلِّ","translation":"অপমানের","audioUrl":"wbw/042_045_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44982,"position":7,"arabic":"يَنظُرُونَ","translation":"তারা দেখবে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_045_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44983,"position":8,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"দিয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_045_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44984,"position":9,"arabic":"طَرْفٍ","translation":"দৃষ্টি","audioUrl":"wbw/042_045_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44985,"position":10,"arabic":"خَفِىٍّۢ ۗ","tra